author: RT
title: Putin & Erdogan to meet in Moscow, visit planned for March 9-10 – Kremlin
text:
Putin & Erdogan to meet in Moscow, visit planned for March 9-10 – Kremlin  25 Edited time: 24 Feb, 2017 11:29 Get short URL FILE PHOTO: Russian President Vladimir Putin (L) and Turkish President Tayyip Erdogan © Osman Orsal / Reuters Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan will meet his Russian counterpart, Vladimir Putin, in Moscow March 9-10, Kremlin spokesman Dmitry Peskov said. 
“I confirm. Negotiations [between Putin and Erdogan] have been planned,” Peskov told journalists.
